I앐 currently not yet really into quake4 editing. I did some maps for quake3
<br />
and haven앖 done anything since that time ! 
<br />
I got q4 some days ago and so far I only played the single player part.
<br />
I really wonder why all shadows in quake are absolutely black !!
<br />
This look absolutely unrealistic.. like in the old times of 3D when there
<br />
was no Radiosity or Global Illumination and people were to lazy to set bounce lights. Did they exclude the Radiosity light calculations from the engine or is this just made to achive some unique style ?</span><span class=sign></span><span class="gensmall"></span>
